                        <desc xml:id="cover">the <emph rend="bold">front cover #1</emph>. Bamboo. Sticker. BnF shelfmark sticker.</desc><desc xml:id="cover">the <emph rend="bold">front cover #2</emph>.</desc><desc xml:id="U1">1 folio = <emph rend="bold">isolated folio</emph>. Tamil foliation 44. 3 lines only on the recto. Contains a verse numbering 25. Verso blank. Although foliated 44, it does not appear to be part of U3, which has no folio foliated 44, but  where the text is continuous from f43 to f45<hi rend="superscript">1</hi>.</desc><desc xml:id="U2">212 folios = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Āraṇiyākāṇṭam &amp; Kiṣkintakāṇṭam</term></emph>. 415 x 30 mm (but some smaller, e.g. f97 = 415 x 25 mm). Tamil foliation 1-212. Unblackened from f82 onwards.

</desc><desc xml:id="U3">133 folios = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Cuntarakāṇṭam</term></emph>. Tamil foliation 1-43, 45<hi rend="superscript">1</hi>, 45<hi rend="superscript">2</hi>, 46-133. </desc><desc xml:id="U4">1 folio = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Cuntarakāṇṭam</term></emph>. Tamil foliation 1. 3 lines only on the recto. Verso blank. This appears to be a draft or duplicate of the beginning of the <term xml:lang="ta">Cuntarakāṇṭam</term>. Stanzas 1 and 2 only, with lacunae (spaces left blank). Found, in the present state of the bundle, between f59 and f60 of U3. </desc><desc xml:id="U5">2 folios = <emph rend="bold">guard leaves</emph>. No foliation. Blank recto verso. These appear to be the front and back guard leaves, misplaced in the bundle. Found, in the present state of the bundle, between f59 and f60 of U3, right after U4. 
</desc><desc xml:id="CoverBack">the <emph rend="bold">front cover</emph>. Forming a set with front cover #2.</desc></collation>
