                  <desc synch="#cover" type="commenting-note">Sticker written by two different hands, on the front single bamboo woodcover . Hand #1 (black ink):<quote><term xml:lang="fr">27 9<hi rend="superscript">b</hi> 1860</term></quote>
Hand #2 (blue ink):
<quote xml:lang="fr">
  <lb n="1"/>N° 2
 <lb n="2"/>Contenant 3 Candams appelés Arania-
   <lb n="3"/>-candam, Kichekinda candam +
  <lb n="4"/>Saundira candam
  <lb n="5"/>2ème partie”
</quote>
Compare with sticker on woodcover of BnF Indien 947.</desc></additions>
